---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import PageHero from '../components/PageHero.astro';
import Breadcrumb from '../components/Breadcrumb.astro';
import SectionHeading from '../components/SectionHeading.astro';

const schema = {
  '@context': 'https://schema.org',
  '@type': 'Service',
  name: 'Insulation Installation',
  provider: { '@type': 'GeneralContractor', name: 'Purpose Construction', url: 'https://purposeconstructionco.com' },
  areaServed: { '@type': 'State', name: 'Texas', containedIn: { '@type': 'Country', name: 'United States' } },
  description: 'Insulation installation across East Texas — spray foam, blown-in, and batt insulation for attics, walls, and crawl spaces with air sealing and R-value assessment for East Texas homes.',
};
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Insulation Installation East Texas | Purpose Construction"
  description="Insulation installation across East Texas — spray foam, blown-in, and batt insulation for attics, walls, and crawl spaces. Purpose Construction improves East Texas home efficiency. Call (936) 555-5555."
  schema={schema}
>
  <Breadcrumb items={[{ label: 'Services', href: '/services' }, { label: 'Exterior Services', href: '/exterior-services' }, { label: 'Insulation Installation', href: '/insulation-installation' }]} />
  <PageHero title="Insulation Installation in East Texas" subtitle="Spray foam, blown-in, and batt insulation for attics, walls, and crawl spaces — reducing cooling loads and improving comfort in East Texas homes year-round." tag="Exterior Service" />

  <section class="section-padding bg-warm-50">
    <div class="container-wide px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-12 lg:grid-cols-2 lg:items-center">
        <div>
          <SectionHeading tag="Insulation Installation" title="The Right Insulation for East Texas's Hot, Humid Climate" />
          <div class="space-y-4 text-base leading-relaxed text-charcoal-600">
            <p>East Texas sits in a mixed-humid climate zone where attic temperatures can exceed 140°F in July and the combination of heat and moisture creates persistent comfort and energy problems in under-insulated homes. Purpose Construction approaches insulation as an integrated system — not just filling cavities, but understanding where the thermal boundary should be and what products perform best in high-humidity conditions specific to the Lufkin area.</p>
            <p>Spray foam insulation is our most powerful tool for hot, humid climates — open-cell foam in attic applications creates an unvented conditioned attic that keeps ductwork within the thermal envelope and dramatically reduces attic temperatures. Blown-in fiberglass or cellulose is highly effective for attic top-up insulation when the existing R-value falls short of current recommendations for East Texas. We also install closed-cell spray foam in crawl spaces and rim joists where moisture management is the primary concern alongside thermal performance.</p>
            <p>We start every insulation project with an R-value assessment to identify where your home is losing the most energy, so you get the best return on your insulation investment — whether you're insulating a new build or upgrading an existing home.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-6 flex gap-4">
            <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">Get a Free Estimate</a>
            <a href="/exterior-services" class="btn-outline">All Exterior Services</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <img src="https://placehold.co/640x480/2a2520/555?text=Insulation+Installation" alt="Insulation installation across East Texas by Purpose Construction" class="rounded-xl shadow-hero" width="640" height="480" loading="lazy" decoding="async" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-padding bg-white border-t border-warm-200">
    <div class="container-wide px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <SectionHeading tag="What's Included" title="Insulation Installation Services" align="center" />
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 sm:grid-cols-3 lg:grid-cols-4">
        {['Spray Foam Insulation', 'Blown-In Insulation', 'Batt Insulation', 'Attic Insulation', 'Wall Insulation', 'Crawl Space Insulation', 'Air Sealing', 'R-Value Assessment'].map(item => (
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 rounded-lg border border-warm-200 bg-warm-50 px-4 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-charcoal-700">
            <span class="h-1.5 w-1.5 flex-shrink-0 rounded-full bg-brand-red" aria-hidden="true"></span>{item}
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-padding-sm bg-warm-50 border-t border-warm-200">
    <div class="container-wide px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <SectionHeading tag="Related Services" title="Related Services" />
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
        {[{ label: 'Window Installation', href: '/window-installation' }, { label: 'Exterior Services', href: '/exterior-services' }, { label: 'New Construction', href: '/new-construction' }].map(link => (
          <a href={link.href} class="rounded-lg border border-warm-200 bg-white px-5 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-charcoal-700 shadow-card hover:border-brand-red-mid hover:text-charcoal-900 transition-all duration-200">{link.label} →</a>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section-padding bg-gradient-red">
    <div class="container-mid px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="display-md text-white mb-4">Lower Your Energy Bills This Summer</h2>
      <p class="mx-auto mb-8 max-w-xl text-base text-white/80">Contact Purpose Construction for a free insulation assessment and estimate. We serve Lufkin and all of East Texas.</p>
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-4 sm:flex-row sm:justify-center">
        <a href="/contact" class="btn-ghost px-8 py-4">Get a Free Quote</a>
        <a href="tel:9365555555" class="text-sm font-semibold text-white/70 hover:text-white transition-colors duration-150">(936) 555-5555</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
